data.description: An expansive family home sitting on 3 acres off Lark and Taylor in Mission with many existing spaces for recreation and room for growth. A large circular driveway leads to the imposing double door entrance of this traditionally built home and its four spacious bedrooms, three full baths, two dining areas, a grand living room with its own brick fireplace, and a spacious kitchen equipped with an island. A large pool and spa with plenty of lounging areas, including a gazebo area perfect for outdoor grilling, lead the way to the many leisure amenities perfect for any family. One of the main amenities is an ample, fully finished, and enclosed barn. Its airy structure allows the flexibility to meet any resident’s needs and can serve as a workshop, multi-vehicle garage, or your very own event center. Dotting the rest of the property are free-standing stables, a detached brick storage shed, and the foundation for a large pavilion. Irrigation is also available on this property.
